title: Join GTA+
headline: Join GTA+
subtitle: Get 6X Rewards on Lunar New Year Stunt Races and More
content:
Join Grand Theft Auto Online’s premium Membership program this week and you’ll receive 6X Rewards on Lunar New Year Stunt Races.

This month you can also get 2X Rewards on Drift Races (stacking to 6X the last week of the month), 2X Rewards on Security Contracts, and Agency discounts.

Membership renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
